	<Language_en_US>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_AVANT_GARDE_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>Eye of the Beholder</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_AVANT_GARDE_HELP">
			<Text>Our tolerance of avante-garde practices has led to a surge in novel and, to some, alarming ideas about what deserves to be called "Art". The luminaries are imbued with righteous fury, and vengeful against the icons of the past.[NEWLINE]Shall we allow these ideas free reign? Or should we... curb their enthusiasm.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_AVANT_GARDE_HELP_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>At the cost of 4 [ICON_HAPPINESS_4] Unhappiness for {4_Turns}. Receive a Great Person of your choice.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_AVANT_GARDE_HELP_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>At the cost of {1_YieldCost}, all [ICON_GREAT_WORK] Great Works generate +2 [ICON_TOURISM] Tourism.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_AVANT_GARDE_HELP_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>Landmarks generate +2 [ICON_TOURISM] Tourism, [ICON_GOLDEN_AGE_POINTS] Golden Age Points, and [ICON_CULTURE] Culture.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_AVANT_GARDE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>The debate shall encourage those coming through our education to question, to think independently, to be the heralds of a new era. Onward!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_AVANT_GARDE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>These introspective calls for the return of foreign Great Works to their places of origin are well founded. Though it may harm our pride and purse, all the world will be enriched by a broader and more accessible corpus.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_AVANT_GARDE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>New art is always necessary to keep us moving forward as a self-critical people. The places in our land dedicated to the celebration of our heritage must also be ready to display that which shall compose our heritage in years to come! Let this new generation be heard!</Text>
		</Row>

		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_BUILDING_IDEOLOGY_AVANT_GARDE_DUMMY">
			<Text></Text>
		</Row>
	</Language_en_US>
